    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/691280/extras/73b9fe86da8b6bc217efef114b7bb428.poster.avif?t=1759307504\" width=616 height=180 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/691280/extras/73b9fe86da8b6bc217efef114b7bb428.webm?t=1759307504\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/691280/extras/73b9fe86da8b6bc217efef114b7bb428.mp4?t=1759307504\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >从崩塌的王国中崛起，挑战难度不断上升的Boss。在每次挑战罪恶化身之前做出艰难抉择，你要牺牲哪部分力量？这就是动作角色扮演游戏《SINNER:Sacrifice for Redemption》。融合经典游戏Boss战和现代动作角色扮演的精髓，再加上细腻的哥特风画面和惊悚叙事，《SINNER:Sacrifice for Redemption》必将给你前所未有的颤栗游戏体验。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >孤独的少年伫立在陌生的彼岸，他是一名灵魂遗忘者，消失的记忆让他疑惑，但是不可阻止的意念驱使着他前进。他是阿当，身怀无法名状的罪恶神秘可怖的力量。他的家园卡瓦尼斯王国正饱受罪恶的摧残，阿当不得不踏上救赎之路，面对让人绝望的试炼。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/691280/extras/64199a4e81a9152c5892edf5624baa68.poster.avif?t=1759307504\" width=616 height=180 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/691280/extras/64199a4e81a9152c5892edf5624baa68.webm?t=1759307504\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/691280/extras/64199a4e81a9152c5892edf5624baa68.mp4?t=1759307504\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >游戏特色</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >面对8个迥异残暴的boss，挑战你的极限</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >牺牲你的力量，在游戏进程中越来越弱小的绝望</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >装备可选武器和道具，适应你的不足</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >困难但是合理的战斗</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >拯救黑暗中悲惨的灵魂，体验多个不同结局</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >多种游戏模式，可重玩性</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/691280/extras/8d4ecb3cc8ba39959e81eeeb259c5794.poster.avif?t=1759307504\" width=616 height=180 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/691280/extras/8d4ecb3cc8ba39959e81eeeb259c5794.webm?t=1759307504\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/691280/extras/8d4ecb3cc8ba39959e81eeeb259c5794.mp4?t=1759307504\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >更多游戏信息与互动请加QQ群：639214393，关注新浪微博@SINNER-救赎之路。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/691280/extras/dc363b7cb6d3098235767043690a5fb6.avif?t=1759307504\" width=575 height=191 /></span></p>",
